## Principles
- Take it slow. One step at a time.
- Document everything visually (screenshots in docs/StepN/).
- No over-engineering. Build what's needed now.
- AI-first where it adds real value, not for show.
- The owner reviews and approves before moving forward.
- Stay vanilla Rails.
